WorkItem.Description:
Why are You using this method for checking type of parameter sending to method, ex. : 
 
	public function setProperties($pValue)
	{
		if ($pValue instanceof PHPExcel_DocumentProperties) {
			$this->_properties = $pValue;
		} else {
			throw new Exception("Invalid PHPExcel_DocumentProperties object passed.");
		}
	}
 
when the recommended method for this (in PHP5 of course) is using Type Hinting ( http://www.php.net/manual/pl/language.oop5.typehinting.php ), for example: 
 
        public function setProperties( PHPExcel_DocumentProperties $pValue)
	{ 
              $this->_properties = $pValue;		
	}
